C\" title=\"Match Statistics\">Doubling TC</a>, <a href=\"/Depth#DiminishingReturns\" title=\"Depth\">Diminishing Returns</a>, <a href=\"/Playing_Strength\" title=\"Playing Strength\">Playing Strength</a>, <a href=\"/Houdini\" title=\"Houdini\">Houdini</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48863\">Type I error in LOS based early stopping rule</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kai Laskos</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 06, 2013 <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49684\">What happens using egbb</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kai Laskos</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 12, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame_Bitbases\" title=\"Endgame Bitbases\">Endgame Bitbases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50266\">Houdini, much weaker engines, and Arpad Elo</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kai Laskos</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 29, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Houdini\" title=\"Houdini\">Houdini</a>, <a href=\"/Pawn_Advantage,_Win_Percentage,_and_Elo\" title=\"Pawn Advantage, Win Percentage, and Elo\">Pawn Advantage, Win Percentage, and Elo</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50452\">STS and the scaling of Houdini and Stockfish</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kai Laskos</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 12, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Houdini\" title=\"Houdini\">Houdini</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2014</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ex